gomodel:SYNGO_3825  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.1: \"Distribution and localization of oligophrenin-1 in the brain\"\n- \"Our studies also showed that oligophrenin-1 is present at presynaptic sites. Endogenous oligophrenin-1 immunolabeling was observed as numerous puncta along axons and overlapped with synaptophysin at some presynaptic terminals (Fig. 1e). \". Experimental description: - \"Medium-density primary hippocampal neuron cultures were prepared from E18 rat embryos as described\"" ;
